489
00:28:51,567 --> 00:28:53,933
TO YOUR MOTHER
AND YOUR FATHER.

490
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:57,234
MY FATHER BEATS ME.

491
00:29:14,367 --> 00:29:15,501
WHERE'S MOM?

492
00:29:15,567 --> 00:29:18,534
