493
00:29:18,601 --> 00:29:22,567
STRESSFUL
CIRCUMSTANCE MOMENT.

494
00:29:22,634 --> 00:29:23,867
YOU WANT
SOMETHING TO EAT?

495
00:29:23,933 --> 00:29:25,200
DAD?

496
