TO JOIN THE ARMY.

497
00:29:29,768 --> 00:29:31,434
LOOK AT ALL THESE FORMS.

498
00:29:31,501 --> 00:29:33,900
DRIVE ANYBODY INSANE,

499
00:29:33,967 --> 00:29:37,768
