BECAUSE THAT'S WHERE
THE BIG MONEY WAS.

501
00:29:41,967 --> 00:29:47,967
TILL THEY TOOK AWAY
MY CLOTHING ALLOWANCE
AND MY COMBAT PAY.

502
00:29:52,668 --> 00:29:55,134
NOW, I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,

503
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,367
