509
00:30:17,501 --> 00:30:19,900
BUT YOU LOVE THIS JOB.

510
00:30:19,967 --> 00:30:22,900
AND I PROMISED
YOUR MAMA A CHANGE.

511
00:30:22,967 --> 00:30:26,134
NOW, YOU WOULDN'T
WANT ME TO BREAK
MY PROMISE, WOULD YA?

512
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,768
DADDY?

513
00:30:27,833 --> 00:30:29,434
YEAH.

514
00:30:29,501 --> 00:30:32,234
