WAS THE YOUNG BOY'S
TEACHER 3 YEARS AGO.

517
00:30:45,668 --> 00:30:46,734
3 YEARS AGO?

518
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:49,000
HE CAME TO HER FIRST,

519
00:30:49,067 --> 00:30:51,467
BUT THEY WERE ALWAYS CLOSE.

520
00:30:51,534 --> 00:30:53,134
HIS PARENTS?

521
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:55,100
I DO NOT KNOW.

522
00:30:55,167 --> 00:30:56,967
WE BROUGHT HIM HOME AND HE...

523
00:30:58,134 --> 00:30:59,900
