BROKE HIS ARM?

525
00:31:01,833 --> 00:31:04,301
HE SAID THAT HE FELL
FROM A SWING SET.

526
00:31:04,367 --> 00:31:06,267
WHEN WE BROUGHT HIM HOME,

527
00:31:06,334 --> 00:31:09,401
HE CHANGED HIS STORY
AND SAID THAT HIS FATHER--

528
00:31:09,467 --> 00:31:10,900
HIS FATHER BEAT HIM.

529
00:31:10,967 --> 00:31:12,768
HIS FATHER'S
NOT HERE NOW.

530
00:31:12,833 --> 00:31:15,567
HE CAME TO
YOUR MS. GERHARDT--

531
00:31:15,634 --> 00:31:16,634
THAT'S RIGHT.

532
00:31:16,701 --> 00:31:18,167
BECAUSE...

533
00:31:18,234 --> 00:31:19,701
YOU SIT HERE, BABY.

534
00:31:19,768 --> 00:31:21,833
