NO, HE'S BEEN
LIVING WITH HIS AUNT
THE LAST 6 MONTHS.

540
00:31:37,100 --> 00:31:39,467
YOU'RE SURE HE DOESN'T LIVE
WITH HIS FATHER AND MOTHER?

541
00:31:39,534 --> 00:31:41,267
