547
00:33:51,499 --> 00:33:53,533
HIS FATHER IS IN IRAQ.

548
00:33:53,599 --> 00:33:56,833
I'M DESIGNATED
LEGAL GUARDIAN
IN THEIR ABSENCE,

549
00:33:56,900 --> 00:33:58,533
